platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: When you’re experiencing anxiety, immediate solutions can be a game changer. Rootd offers instant relief with content to help you work through a panic attack or find a moment of mindfulness. Find support through journaling, breathing exercises, visualizations, and more. Plus take a weekly anxiety questionnaire and see your average monthly results to help you track progress over time.
當你感到焦慮時，即時應對問題或能徹底改變狀況。不妨透過這款 App 的內容克服恐慌或練習靜觀，以此及時紓緩情緒。
When you’re experiencing anxiety, immediate solutions can be a game changer. Get instant relief from content that helps you work through a panic attack or find a moment of mindfulness.
當你感到焦慮時，能否獲得即時的幫助非常關鍵。無論你是會焦慮恐慌或想練習正念冥想，這款 App 都能提供你立即的紓緩內容。
